â—  Powerful Lead Management Tool

    â—‹ Lower search triggers on LinkedIn to avoid getting search limitation while prospecting
    â—‹ View tagged profiles directly within LinkedRadar for easy lead management.
    â—‹ Search tagged profiles and lists to quickly find ideal prospects for your outreach campaigns.

    â—‹ Instantly send personalized invites powered by ChatGPT

â— A Safe LinkedIn Leads Generator
       â—‹ Safety is first focus of LinkedRadar - it is designed for 100% simulation of human activity

    â—‹ Compatible with Personal, Sales Navigator, Premium and Recruiter Lite accounts.
    â—‹ Personalize outreach with AI-powered icebreakers, based on targeted audiences LinkedIn's profile information
    â—‹ Save more than 80% of your prospecting time and increase 10x acceptance rate with GPT-4 personalized invitations. 

â—  LinkedIn Automated Messaging
    â—‹ Send mass messages to hundreds of 1st connections in bulk safely
    â—‹ Personalize engagement with industry, education, experience etc. extracted from LinkedIn profiles
    â—‹ AI-powered follow-up messages for continued conversations

â— Huge Library of Business Message Templates - Pre-Set & Customizable
       â—‹ Create high converting templates with AI assistance
       â—‹ Increase response rates for automated messaging
